:

1. *Mislite* li da će se to desiti? (Do you think this will happen?)
2. *Mislio* sam da će se sve dobro završiti. (I thought everything would end well.)
3. *Misleći* o svemu, shvatio sam da moram da se spremim. (Thinking about everything, I realized I had to get ready.)
4. *Mislite* li da je to moguće? (Do you think that's possible?)
5. *Mislilo* se da će to biti lako. (It was thought that it would be easy.)